# 🤝 Contributing to MEV Protection Shield Bot

We welcome contributions that enhance the performance, reliability, or monitoring capabilities of the bot.

## 🧩 How to Contribute

1. Fork the repository
2. Clone your fork (`git clone https://github.com/your-username/mev-shield.git`)
3. Create a new branch (`git checkout -b feature/your-feature`)
4. Commit your changes (`git commit -m 'Add your feature'`)
5. Push to your branch (`git push origin feature/your-feature`)
6. Open a Pull Request

## 🧪 Areas of Interest

- Advanced RPC metrics  
- Wallet activity analysis  
- Validator performance analytics  
- Discord/Slack integrations  
- UI dashboard layer

---

💡 *Let’s build safer blockchain systems—together.*
